@startuml
' Domain: notes  |  mode: full
' Edge legend: --> ORM relationship()   ..> FK-only (no relationship)
hide empty members
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam ClassBorderColor #888888
skinparam ClassBackgroundColor #FAFAFA

class EntityNote <<entity_notes>> {
  +id : int <<PK>>
  +entity_type : str
  +entity_id : int
  +note : text
  +created_by : int? <<FK→users>>
  +created_at : datetime
  +updated_at : datetime?
  +deleted_at : datetime?
  +deleted_by : int? <<FK→users>>
}

' FK-only links (no ORM relationship declared):
EntityNote ..> User : created_by
EntityNote ..> User : deleted_by

@enduml